features: 【Kindly Reminder】 To avoid burned, please wear gloves and ensure that the waterproof washer is properly installed to avoid air and water leaks.

【Powerful Steamer For Cleaning】with 2500W high power, this instant home steam cleaner will be ready in 15 seconds. The steamer generates 221°F/105°C and 3BAR high temperature pressured flow of steam that will deeply clear out stubborn grease, dirt and stains for wide range of items and surfaces to help you create a clean atmosphere around you.

【Flexible & Portable】AUXCO steam cleaner is compact and will not occupy too much space for convenient handling and storage. With a 2m steam tube and 1.5m extended power cord, the steamer is a convenient cleaning assistant that will meet your home and outdoor cleaning needs. The high temperature, high pressure steam will easily penetrate deep corners and crevices for thorough cleaning.

【1200ml Large Water Tank】The portable steam cleaner features 1200ml large capacity water tank which allows you to perform cleaning away from the water source without worrying about refilling, improving your work efficiency. The 6-gear knob allows you to adjust the steam outlet, reach different steam water content and meet your different cleaning needs while saving on water as compared to traditional hand cleaning.

【Multi-surface Cleaning】With 3 different brush heads, the steamer is ideal for cleaning virtually any surface in your kitchen, bathroom or furniture. Use thoroughly clean dirt, grime and stains on walls, microwave, oven, refrigerator, sink, Cook top, windows, washing machine and even as a car steam cleaner for car detailing, which will save you a ton more on car wash!

【Excellent Service】We are so confident in AUXCO steam cleaner quality. We provide you 2 Years-Warranty with satisfactory after-sales service. If you have any questions, please contact us, and we will solve it within 24hrs (No Need to Return Product). We're always here.
